      "u16:0",
      "u8:0",
      "u8:0",
      "ルナ",
      "「わたしもそう思ったんだけど、なんか訳してたら変になる\\n　の」"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 123,
    "index": 6,
    "value": [
      "u16:1",
      "u8:0",
      "　確かに変だ。"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 142,
    "index": 7,
    "value": [
      "u16:2",
      "u8:0",
      "　軍政（military government）や民事（civil affairs）が\\n支配する期間（the period of time）は《is maintained》\\n──維持される？　《will vary》──変化するだろう？"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 309,
    "index": 8,
    "value": [
      "u16:3",
      "u8:0",
      "　──変だ。"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 326,
    "index": 9,
    "value": [
      "u16:4",
      "u8:0",
      "　もう一度おれは読み返してみた。"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 363,
    "index": 10,
    "value": [
      "u16:5",
      "u8:0",
      "　The period of time during which military government \\nor civil affairs control is maintained will vary,depen\\nding on whether military operations are continuing．"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 532,
    "index": 11,
    "value": [
      "u16:6",
      "u8:0",
      "　《military government》や《civil affairs》民事がcont\\nrolする──"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 604,
    "index": 12,
    "value": [
      "u16:7",
      "u8:0",
      "　ふと思った。"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 623,
    "index": 13,
    "value": [
      "u16:8",
      "u8:0",
      "　controlって、動詞か？　こいつ、名詞なんじゃないのか？"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 683,
    "index": 14,
    "value": [
      "u16:9",
      "u8:0",
      "　《military government》や《civil affairs control》が\\n《is maintained》される──"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 771,
    "index": 15,
    "value": [
      "u16:10",
      "u8:0",
      "　──頭のなかで、意味がつながった。"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "42",
    "offset": 812,
    "index": 16,
    "value": [
      "u16:11",
      "u8:0",
      "u8:0",
      "花丸",
      "「will varyだよ」"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "41",
    "offset": 840,
    "index": 17,
    "value": [
      "u16:12",
      "u8:0",
      "　おれは問題集を指差した。"
    ]
  },
  {
    "op": "42",
    "offset": 871,
    "index": 18,
    "value": [
      "u16:13",
      "u8:0",
      "u8:0",
      "花丸",
      "「controlは名詞。《military government》で１つの名詞。\\n　《civil affairs control》で１つの名詞。民事管理」"
    ]
  },
